    title: "The Capital Stack in Property Development: How to Structure Your Funding",
    metaTitle: "Capital Stack in Property Development | UK Guide",
    metaDescription: "Learn how the capital stack works in UK property development. Understand senior debt, mezzanine, equity layers and how to structure funding for maximum returns.",
