    metaTitle: "Development Finance Exit Strategies | UK Guide",
    metaDescription: "Plan your development finance exit strategy. Learn about unit sales, refinancing, bulk sales, and how your exit choice affects loan terms and lender appetite.",
    excerpt: "A comprehensive guide to exit strategies in development finance, covering individual sales, refinancing, bulk disposals, and how to choose the right approach for your scheme.",
